name: Maeve
description:
This is Maeve.
Maeve has been the building Co-Op President for 27 years.
Maeve always seems to be in the elevator.
Everyone in the building tries to avoid Maeve.
You would do well to avoid Maeve.
Maeve's son, Anthony, is 27.
Anthony still lives at home.
